The paper discusses the adaptation of the Layer-wise Relevance Propagation (LRP) technique for explaining the predictions of feed-forward networks to the LSTM architecture used for sequential data modeling and forecasting. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
